views.text: Getting ready for the new school year? Check out this Challenge for help getting prepared and a fun motivation boost! Plus, there's a chance to win gems and subscription prizes!
Delete distracting and time wasting apps.
Get a healthy morning & evening routine, which will help you to get more energy and boost your day.
With this challenge you schedule what you will do the next week on every day.
Watch "Worlds of Ursula K. Le Guin"

The PBS documentary [Worlds of Ursula K. Le Guin](https://www.pbs.org/wnet/americanmasters/worlds-of-ursula-k-le-guin-full-film/11632/) is free to stream until August 30th. Watch the documentary to learn more about this important author.
